 spatial distribution of LBVs therefore is consistent with the\nstandard picture of massive star evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Oct 2018 03:12:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Nov 2018 18:46:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 3 Jan 2019 18:31:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-04"}
