ions and\npenetration ratio of mmWave communication devices in learning and operation\nphases are different.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Oct 2018 07:31:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 22 Mar 2019 08:59:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-25"}
