acy, settling time, energy consumption and regeneration), over comparable\nschemes where either stiffness or damping are fixed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Oct 2018 10:20:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Jul 2019 11:31:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 10 Feb 2020 03:52:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-30"}
